<br>
&quot;I don't beleive this&quot; Luthair muttered to himself. &quot;I may be of only the 16th rank... but this is just demeaning. Oh well, he will be useful later.&quot; Luthair was supossed to meet up with a paladin at the point on which he sat. Nursing some cheap liquor that he stole from aviaks. The paladins name was Garyth. He was supposed to be quite rich despite the fact that most paladins took a vow of poverty. This paladin was going to help him with honing his skills. On unsuspecting aviaks. Suddenly he was shocked out of his self pity by a terrified scream filling his mind. Everyone had telling stones, and Luthair was cursing into his. &quot;What is it?&quot; he shouted angrily into his telling stone.<br>
&quot;You didn't say there were gnolls here!&quot; sounded the wailing voice of Garyth in Luthairs head. <br>
&quot;Well then... fight them!&quot; the rogue was becoming angrier by the second. <br>
&quot;I kinda' can't... I am only of the 12th rank.&quot; <br>
&quot;WHAT? Ok...ok... go around the gnolls and swim to me.&quot;<br>
&quot;I swim like a lead weight.&quot;<br>
The veins on Luthairs head began to swell. By the time he had gotten his idea, his head resembled a spider. <br>
&quot;I have a plan, there is a cliff near you. Go onto the edge of the cliff and wait for me.&quot;<br>
The furious rogue darted into action. After slaying a nearby aviak and stealing the boat it was guarding he rowed it within a stones throw of the cliff. <br>
&quot;Ok... I want you to jump in the water and swim to the boat.&quot;<br>
&quot;What?&quot;<br>
&quot;DO IT!&quot; <br>
At that moment the paladin jumped away from the cliff. Yet not far enough away, with a sickening crunch the half elf slammed into the rocks near the shore and his limp body rolled into the boat. Minutes later he awoke. <br>
&quot;Aaaah! Dark elf! Prepare to taste cold steel!&quot; <br>
Luthair nimbly dodged the confused paladins blows before finally explained that he was Luthair.<br>
&quot;So, anyway... lets hope yer good halfelf. We have killin' to do.&quot;<br>
<br>
-Luthair <br>
Dark elf Rogue<br>
16th rank<br>
Lords of the Dark Realm<br>
Bristlebane Server.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=763.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.showMessage?topicID=765.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.emailToFriend?topicID=767.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.threadControl?topicID=767.topic><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/shpics/closeThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=767.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousebythefireplace.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=767.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="thesafehouseloungegeneraldiscussion">Main Lounge<option value="thesafehousecontractsbountiesjobsquestsetc">News Bulletin<option value="thesafehousetrainingstudioqafornewbies">Training Studio<option value="thesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers">The Back Alley<option value="thesafehousefrm13">Quests of Norrath<option value="thesafehousetherootcellar">The Root Cellar<option value="thesafehouselaboratory">Laboratory<option value="thesafehousefr